Privacy Policy
for the Dudel Draw app, property of Silly Little Apps LLC
Last Updated: June 12, 2023
Your Consent
Dudel (hereinafter referred to as "we," "us," or "our") takes your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share information about you when you use our iOS app (the "App"). We respect the privacy of our users, especially children under 13 years old. By using our services (including this website and our app for various devices), you consent to this privacy policy.
1. Information We Collect When you use our App, we may collect the following information:
We want to assure you that our App does not collect any personal information from you. We do not gather, store, or track any data that can be used to personally identify you, such as your name, address, location, email address, or phone number.
As our App does not collect any personal information, we do not automatically collect any data about your usage of the App. We do not use cookies, web beacons, or any other tracking technologies to track your activities.
2. Third-Party Services
Our App does not integrate with any third-party services or platforms that may collect or process your personal information.
3. Sharing of Your Information
We do not sell or share your information with third parties for their marketing purposes.
4. Security of Your Information
We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no security measure is perfect, and we cannot guarantee the security of your information.
5. Children's Privacy
Our App is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13.
6. Contact us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please contact us at contact@sillylittleapps.com